==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sloughy
<hw>Slough"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Resembling, or of the
nature of, a slough, or the dead matter which separates from living
flesh.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sloven</ent>⟦br⟧
